wiki.summary: Lil Uzi Vert's song "Futsal Shuffle 2020" was released through Atlantic, Warner, and WEA on December 13, 2019 and debuted at number 5 on the Billboard Hot 100. The song was teased ahead of its release with a preview of the rapper and their friends performing the dance with the same name. The song has been described as an "upbeat banger" incorporating EDM synths and bass-heavy loops, while lyrically it "delivers cocky lines about private jets, money, designer labels, and stealing other dudes' girls". wiki.content: Lil Uzi Vert's song "Futsal Shuffle 2020" was released through Atlantic, Warner, and WEA on December 13, 2019 and debuted at number 5 on the Billboard Hot 100. The song was teased ahead of its release with a preview of the rapper and their friends performing the dance with the same name. The song has been described as an "upbeat banger" incorporating EDM synths and bass-heavy loops, while lyrically it "delivers cocky lines about private jets, money, designer labels, and stealing other dudes' girls". An official video was released on January 6, 2020, directed by Jay Weneta, featuring the titular "Futsal Shuffle" dance and vibrant visual effects. Lil Uzi Vert's "Futsal Shuffle 2020" has become a cultural phenomenon, taking over 2020 with both its captivating song and dance. It has been praised for its unique sound and its clever lyrics, and is Lil Uzi Vert's highest charting solo song. The accompanying dance has become widely popular, with the "Futsal Shuffle" being shared on social media platforms around the world. Along with the song, the dance has become a testament to the impact of Lil Uzi Vert's music. Read more on Last.fm.
